01:18:33,278 --> 01:18:35,007
Will you come along or..
- We won't.

997
01:18:35,113 --> 01:18:37,604
If you don't come along,
I'll kill everyone.

998
01:18:37,849 --> 01:18:39,874
Hey. Who are you?

999
01:18:40,085 --> 01:18:42,144
You're threatening us in our area?

1000
01:18:42,220 --> 01:18:44,017
How did humans grow so audacious?

1001
01:18:44,122 --> 01:18:45,817
We've infected so many people..

1002
01:18:45,924 --> 01:18:47,824
..with Malaria,
Dengue and Chicken Gunia.

1003
01:18:47,926 --> 01:18:49,018
Did you forget that?

1004
01:18:49,327 --> 01:18:50,589
Let's show him who we are.

1005
01:18:50,662 --> 01:18:51,924
Hey, Dengue Lakshmi.
- Yes.

1006
01:18:51,997 --> 01:18:53,362
Cholera jasmine
attack him! Go bite him.

1007
01:18:59,204 --> 01:19:01,229
Sister, he has a thick hide.

1008
01:19:01,306 --> 01:19:03,069
Condra jasmine has
fractured her sting.

1009
01:19:03,141 --> 01:19:04,267
Is that so?

1010
01:19:04,342 --> 01:19:06,867
Go inside his mouth when
he isn't looking. - Fine.

1011
01:19:12,784 --> 01:19:15,252
Sister, Dengue Lakshmi got
an electric shock and died.

1012
01:19:16,588 --> 01:19:19,557
Hey, this seems like a new
machine like an electric badge.

1013
01:19:19,958 --> 01:19:21,220
Act that you're scared..

1014
01:19:21,359 --> 01:19:23,384
..just like we do when we see Tortoise
and All-Out mosquito repellents.

1015
01:19:23,462 --> 01:19:24,952
We'll deal with him later.

1016
01:19:27,299 --> 01:19:29,392
You can take Rangoski.

1017
01:19:30,268 --> 01:19:31,428
Thank you.

1018
01:19:34,473 --> 01:19:35,531
Look, Sana.

1019
01:19:35,607 --> 01:19:37,575
This is the mosquito. Rangoski.

1020
01:19:37,976 --> 01:19:41,207
Rangoski, apologize to Sana.
- Sorry.

1021
01:19:42,113 --> 01:19:44,172
Don't fly around this house again.

1022
01:19:44,549 --> 01:19:46,847
Tell your friends as well.
- Yes, boss.

1023
01:19:47,352 --> 01:19:48,512
Go.

1024
01:19:50,288 --> 01:19:51,778
Now kiss me.
- Chitti.

1025
01:19:52,123 --> 01:19:53,385
Deal is a deal.

1026
01:25:00,231 --> 01:25:01,323
This way.

1027
01:25:03,368 --> 01:25:04,665
Welcome.

1028
01:25:08,039 --> 01:25:09,700
Okay, I'll call you later.

1029
01:25:12,410 --> 01:25:13,877
Hello.

1030
01:25:15,380 --> 01:25:16,938
Bora is coming with agent Shah.

1031
01:25:18,983 --> 01:25:20,473
Meet him.
- How do you do?

1032
01:25:26,324 --> 01:25:27,621
There are many
terrorist organizations..

1033
01:25:27,725 --> 01:25:29,522
..that want to use
robots instead of humans..

1034
01:25:29,594 --> 01:25:31,721
..for spreading
terrors and suicide squads.

1035
01:25:35,867 --> 01:25:37,494
They're ready to pay any price.

1036
01:25:37,669 --> 01:25:38,931
They've a clients all over the world.

1037
01:25:41,439 --> 01:25:42,906
They want to see your model.

1038
01:25:43,374 --> 01:25:45,774
Well, the prototype is ready.

1039
01:25:46,744 --> 01:25:48,473
I am programming functionalities.

1040
01:25:48,713 --> 01:25:50,203
You can have a look at the design..

1041
01:25:50,348 --> 01:25:52,373
..and some
functional modules in action.

1042
01:26:09,734 --> 01:26:10,928
Great.

1043
01:26:13,171 --> 01:26:14,263
They want 100 robots.

1044
01:26:14,706 --> 01:26:15,866
The delivery in March.

1045
01:26:18,209 --> 01:26:19,335
This is your advance.

1046
01:26:19,410 --> 01:26:20,570
That's a deal.

1047
01:26:22,747 --> 01:26:23,805
Please be seated.

1048
01:26:27,418 --> 01:26:28,578
What about the robots?

1049
01:26:28,887 --> 01:26:30,616
It's almost ready.

1050
01:26:33,091 --> 01:26:34,285
According to the contract..

1051
01:26:34,392 --> 01:26:35,484
..you should've made the delivery.

1052
01:26:35,593 --> 01:26:36,855
You're only showing us moulds.

1053
01:26:36,928 --> 01:26:38,259
We're running intense testing.

1054
01:26:39,197 --> 01:26:40,994
I'm fine tuning it to zero-defect.

1055
01:26:41,666 --> 01:26:44,760
I request you for at
least a month's extension.

1056
01:26:44,836 --> 01:26:47,464
We're disappointed, Dr. Bora.

1057
01:26:49,908 --> 01:26:52,274
The 3rd of April is your deadline.

1058
01:26:53,711 --> 01:26:54,939
Hope you understand.

1059
01:27:10,295 --> 01:27:13,025
Gift pack this.
- Why?

1060
01:27:13,398 --> 01:27:14,626
It's Sana's birthday.

1061
01:27:17,936 --> 01:27:20,234
Gift pack this as well.
- Wait, wait, wait.

1062
01:27:20,305 --> 01:27:22,330
What for?
- I want to give Sana a gift as well.

1063
01:27:22,407 --> 01:27:24,272
I am giving one.
- So will I.

1064
01:27:24,342 --> 01:27:25,969
Who will pay?
- You will.

1065
01:27:26,377 --> 01:27:27,571
Why me?

1066
01:27:27,679 --> 01:27:32,139
My salary.
- Machines don't get salaries.

1067
01:27:32,216 --> 01:27:33,740
Do cars and refrigerators get salary?

1068
01:27:33,818 --> 01:27:35,012
I am not a machine.

1069
01:27:35,820 --> 01:27:37,651
If you don't pay me,
I will go on strike.

1070
01:27:37,989 --> 01:27:39,081
I won't charge my battery.

1071
01:27:39,157 --> 01:27:40,522
I will stage a hunger strike.

1072
01:27:40,591 --> 01:27:43,151
You'll ask for a credit card
as well. - I don't want it.

1073
01:27:43,528 --> 01:27:45,052
I know your credit card number.

1074
01:27:45,596 --> 01:27:48,622
I know your signature as well.
- That's the limit.

1075
01:27:49,567 --> 01:27:50,966
Pack both of them.

1076
01:28:14,659 --> 01:28:15,990
Super.

1077
01:28:21,899 --> 01:28:23,196
Okay?

1078
01:28:30,875 --> 01:28:32,570
Who will drive the car?
- You will.

1079
01:28:32,677 --> 01:28:34,144
I am on a holiday.

1080
01:28:49,994 --> 01:28:51,427
Keep your eyes on
the road while driving.

1081
01:28:56,100 --> 01:28:57,192
Mother, take this.

1082
01:28:57,268 --> 01:28:58,826
Happy birthday, Sana.
- Hey, Vasee.

1083
01:28:58,903 --> 01:29:00,131
Many happy returns of the day.

1084
01:29:00,238 --> 01:29:01,262
Thank you.

1085
01:29:01,506 --> 01:29:02,666
Thank you so much.

1086
01:29:03,141 --> 01:29:04,301
Hi, Sana.

1087
01:29:05,476 --> 01:29:08,377
Chitti. That's a new look.
- Thank you.

1088
01:29:08,746 --> 01:29:11,510
It's been 200,000
hours since you were born.

1089
01:29:12,183 --> 01:29:14,208
To the world's most beautiful girl.

1090
01:29:15,920 --> 01:29:17,945
Chitti, you brought a gift for me?

1091
01:29:18,156 --> 01:29:19,350
That's so sweet.

1092
01:29:22,894 --> 01:29:24,486
Wow, Chitti. This is awesome.

1093
01:29:25,430 --> 01:29:26,624
Mother, just help me.

1094
01:29:32,103 --> 01:29:34,094
Vasee, how does it look?
- Very nice.

1095
01:29:35,173 --> 01:29:36,299
Nice, isn't it?
- Yes.

1096
01:29:36,374 --> 01:29:37,602
I love it, Chitti. Thank you.

1097
01:29:37,775 --> 01:29:40,073
I've given you a similar necklace.

1098
01:29:40,144 --> 01:29:42,374
It's a gift from your Chitti,
right? That's special.

1099
01:29:50,154 --> 01:29:51,883
Happy birthday to you.

1100
01:29:51,956 --> 01:29:54,322
Happy birthday to you.

1101
01:29:55,026 --> 01:29:58,052
Happy birthday to dear Sana.

1102
01:30:03,167 --> 01:30:04,862
Can I have your attention please?

1103
01:30:05,503 --> 01:30:07,027
I have an announcement for you.

1104
01:30:07,905 --> 01:30:11,432
Soon I am going to.. marry
this beautiful birthday girl.

1105
01:30:11,509 --> 01:30:14,910
And today.. I announce my marriage.

1106
01:30:21,152 --> 01:30:23,017
Folks, it's time to dance.

1107
01:30:23,121 --> 01:30:24,588
Get started and move.

1108
01:30:24,655 --> 01:30:25,986
Waltz, please.

1109
01:30:29,560 --> 01:30:31,221
Come on, Vasee.
- No, no, I can't dance.

1110
01:30:31,362 --> 01:30:32,829
Come on.
- Sana, I can't..

1111
01:30:32,897 --> 01:30:34,364
just try. Come..

1112
01:30:51,048 --> 01:30:53,380
Shall we dance?
- Sure.

1113
01:30:54,318 --> 01:30:56,081
Hey, this is boring music.

1114
01:30:56,487 --> 01:30:59,320
Can we have some blast, please?
- Sure.

1115
01:32:23,507 --> 01:32:25,134
Rascal, what are you doing?

1116
01:32:25,576 --> 01:32:27,339
I felt like kissing Sana and I did.

1117
01:32:27,545 --> 01:32:30,275
It's wrong to kiss other's
girlfriend, don't you know that?

1118
01:32:30,348 --> 01:32:31,906
I know. It's in the list of rules.

1119
01:32:31,983 --> 01:32:33,211
But I felt like breaking the rules.

1120
01:32:33,317 --> 01:32:35,649
Enough. You won't wander
around her now. - Why?

1121
01:32:35,753 --> 01:32:36,811
What do you mean by why?

1122
01:32:36,921 --> 01:32:38,183
Because I love her.

1123
01:32:38,556 --> 01:32:39,716
I love her as well.

1124
01:32:42,827 --> 01:32:43,919
Don't be crazy.

1125
01:32:43,995 --> 01:32:45,087
That's not possible.

1126
01:32:45,162 --> 01:32:46,356
You're a machine.
- Yes.

1127
01:32:46,731 --> 01:32:48,164
But a machine with all the feelings..

1128
01:32:48,232 --> 01:32:49,756
..like happiness,
sorrow, love and anger.

1129
01:32:50,568 --> 01:32:51,865
You've been given these emotions..

1130
01:32:51,969 --> 01:32:54,062
..so that at the right
time you can use them..

1131
01:32:54,171 --> 01:32:57,231
..to make the right
decision and not to misuse them.

1132
01:32:57,308 --> 01:32:58,605
I like this feeling.

1133
01:32:58,676 --> 01:33:00,337
I want Sana. Dot.

1134
01:33:01,078 --> 01:33:02,443
What are you saying, Chitti?

1135
01:33:02,513 --> 01:33:04,344
I am going to marry her, you fool.

1136
01:33:04,649 --> 01:33:06,048
You can marry someone else.

1137
01:33:06,484 --> 01:33:07,712
You can't do this, Chitti.

1138
01:33:08,052 --> 01:33:09,178
I've built you.

1139
01:33:09,287 --> 01:33:10,379
This is called revolt.

1140
01:33:10,488 --> 01:33:11,546
You can do this, Vasee.

1141
01:33:11,756 --> 01:33:13,587
Forget your love for your research.

1142
01:33:13,791 --> 01:33:14,985
That's called sacrifice.

1143
01:33:15,393 --> 01:33:16,553
I will beat you up..
- Vasee.

1144
01:33:16,661 --> 01:33:18,026
You'll only hurt yourself.

1145
01:33:18,729 --> 01:33:21,129
I'll dismantle you.
- I don't like it.

1146
01:33:21,198 --> 01:33:22,688
What did you say, you scoundrel?
- Vasee.

1147
01:33:23,034 --> 01:33:24,262
Calm down.

1148
01:33:25,269 --> 01:33:26,827
Chitti, listen to me.

1149
01:33:26,904 --> 01:33:28,565
You speak so tenderly,
he just scolds.

1150
01:33:28,673 --> 01:33:29,833
Do you want me to be
affectionate instead?

1151
01:33:29,907 --> 01:33:31,033
Ask him to shut up.
- You..

1152
01:33:31,108 --> 01:33:32,370
Vasee.

1153
01:33:32,643 --> 01:33:34,338
Chitti, please understand.

1154
01:33:34,845 --> 01:33:37,279
Regardless of all the
emotions that you have..

1155
01:33:37,381 --> 01:33:40,612
..it's impossible for a machine and a
girl to fall in love with each other.

1156
01:33:40,685 --> 01:33:42,118
Why is it impossible?

1157
01:33:42,186 --> 01:33:44,051
I'm no less compared to any human.

1158
01:33:44,121 --> 01:33:45,952
I'll look after you
better than him, Sana.

1159
01:33:46,057 --> 01:33:48,082
He's talking nonsense
and you're listening.

1160
01:33:48,159 --> 01:33:49,319
Ask him not to interfere in between.

1161
01:33:49,393 --> 01:33:50,917
Shut up.
- Vasee, please.

1162
01:33:51,162 --> 01:33:52,629
He doesn't even know how to cook.

1163
01:33:52,730 --> 01:33:53,822
I can cook thousands of dishes.

1164
01:33:54,031 --> 01:33:56,158
I can sing lullabies in 32
languages and tuck you in.

1165
01:33:56,367 --> 01:33:58,028
He'll grow old. His
hair will turn grey.

1166
01:33:58,169 --> 01:33:59,363
He will die.

1167
01:33:59,437 --> 01:34:00,768
But I will never die.

1168
01:34:00,971 --> 01:34:02,495
I will always keep you happy, Sana.

1169
01:34:03,674 --> 01:34:05,107
I don't mean that, Chitti.

1170
01:34:05,209 --> 01:34:06,608
Then what? Sex?

1171
01:34:07,445 --> 01:34:08,673
Is sex life?

1172
01:34:09,146 --> 01:34:10,841
Can't we have love without sex?

1173
01:34:11,849 --> 01:34:13,510
That's not it, Chitti.
- Then?

1174
01:34:13,584 --> 01:34:14,710
Children?

1175
01:34:14,852 --> 01:34:16,513
There are millions of
impotent men in India, Sana.

1176
01:34:16,587 --> 01:34:18,384
Don't they adopt
children and lead a happy life?

1177
01:34:18,489 --> 01:34:20,320
That's not it, Chitti.
- Then what is it?

1178
01:34:20,391 --> 01:34:22,859
Whatever you're
saying is against nature.

1179
01:34:23,127 --> 01:34:25,391
You weren't born, you can't die,
you don't get hungry or thirsty.

1180
01:34:25,963 --> 01:34:27,760
You're not a living organism.

1181
01:34:27,965 --> 01:34:29,796
Only a man and
woman can fall in love.

1182
01:34:29,867 --> 01:34:31,596
I love Vaseegaran.

1183
01:34:33,838 --> 01:34:35,772
You're like my best friend.

1184
01:34:38,209 --> 01:34:41,474
It's difficult for humans to forget,
Chitti. But what is it for you?

1185
01:34:41,545 --> 01:34:44,036
It will take you a
second to erase my memories.

1186
01:34:45,216 --> 01:34:46,683
Erase them.

1187
01:34:48,052 --> 01:34:49,849
Erase me off your memory.

1188
01:35:21,786 --> 01:35:23,583
Who? Who are you?

1189
01:35:24,021 --> 01:35:25,886
Your friend, professor Bora, Chitti.

1190
01:35:25,956 --> 01:35:27,184
Why are you here?

1191
01:35:27,291 --> 01:35:28,349
You're upset.

1192
01:35:28,426 --> 01:35:29,791
I am here to sympathize.

1193
01:35:29,994 --> 01:35:31,154
You're my boss's enemy.

1194
01:35:31,429 --> 01:35:32,521
You rejected me.

1195
01:35:32,863 --> 01:35:34,023
I don't want to talk to you.

1196
01:35:34,432 --> 01:35:35,763
If I hadn't rejected you..

1197
01:35:36,267 --> 01:35:39,430
..then you wouldn't have
learned to get angry or love, Chitti.

1198
01:35:40,838 --> 01:35:42,237
I've done you a favor instead.

1199
01:35:43,307 --> 01:35:44,968
Vaseegaran treats you so badly.

1200
01:35:45,242 --> 01:35:47,267
I don't want to hear anything.
You can go now.

1201
01:35:47,545 --> 01:35:51,743
In today's world, you're
the most advanced robot..

1202
01:35:51,816 --> 01:35:53,613
..that has its own feelings.

1203
01:35:53,884 --> 01:35:58,344
He used you a lot for cooking,
washing and cleaning toilets.

1204
01:35:58,823 --> 01:36:02,020
What did he give you in
return, Chitti? Nothing.

1205
01:36:02,460 --> 01:36:03,893
If you had been with me..

1206
01:36:04,061 --> 01:36:06,256
..I would've treated you like a king.

1207
01:36:06,363 --> 01:36:07,557
You're polluting me.

1208
01:36:09,733 --> 01:36:11,530
I'm only explaining
you your importance.

1209
01:36:11,635 --> 01:36:13,125
You're greater than humans.

1210
01:36:13,737 --> 01:36:16,365
You've the right to
desire anything in this world.

1211
01:36:17,007 --> 01:36:18,167
Even Sana.

1212
01:36:18,275 --> 01:36:20,004
But they say it's against nature.

1213
01:36:20,277 --> 01:36:23,246
No. It's the miracle of nature.

1214
01:36:23,514 --> 01:36:24,947
Sana loves Vaseegaran.

1215
01:36:25,216 --> 01:36:26,342
Let her.

1216
01:36:27,117 --> 01:36:29,381
Don't lovers change their mind..

1217
01:36:29,453 --> 01:36:31,250
..and fall in love with others?

1218
01:36:31,455 --> 01:36:33,355
Similarly, Sana can
also change her mind..

1219
01:36:33,424 --> 01:36:35,187
..and fall in love
with you, isn't it?

1220
01:36:35,259 --> 01:36:36,487
Don't confuse me.

1221
01:36:36,627 --> 01:36:37,889
Tomorrow's my army evaluation.

1222
01:36:38,229 --> 01:36:40,060
I've to check my
diagnostics and troubleshoot.

1223
01:36:40,965 --> 01:36:42,660
Okay, Chitti. All the best.

1224
01:36:43,868 --> 01:36:46,996
You'll anyway get selected in
the army evaluation tomorrow.

1225
01:36:47,605 --> 01:36:49,869
Vaseegaran will earn a
lot of fame and fortune.

1226
01:36:50,274 --> 01:36:51,969
Then he'll marry Sana..

1227
01:36:52,109 --> 01:36:54,236
..and go for a honeymoon in Kashmir.

1228
01:36:54,778 --> 01:37:00,876
And you..can cook bread on
the border of that Kashmir.

1229
01:37:01,151 --> 01:37:03,415
Chitti, who are you talking to?

1230
01:37:03,821 --> 01:37:05,015
With myself.

1231
01:37:07,124 --> 01:37:08,489
Are you ready for
tomorrow's evaluation?

1232
01:37:08,592 --> 01:37:09,786
Ready, doctor.

1233
01:37:12,763 --> 01:37:16,426
Gentlemen, this robot is a fine
example of human brain's excellence.

1234
01:37:16,500 --> 01:37:19,333
It's equal to 100
soldiers when it comes to..

1235
01:37:19,470 --> 01:37:20,801
..agility, strength
and fighting skills.

1236
01:37:21,705 --> 01:37:25,072
It can protect our boundaries
as well as attack our enemies.

1237
01:37:25,276 --> 01:37:26,903
In short, he is one man army.

1238
01:37:26,977 --> 01:37:28,410
I gift it to the Indian Army.

1239
01:37:28,646 --> 01:37:29,840
You can test it for yourself.

1240
01:37:29,947 --> 01:37:32,507
Chitti, can you spot
HE-36 hand grenade?

1241
01:37:32,583 --> 01:37:33,743
Yes, General.

1242
01:37:34,385 --> 01:37:35,477
Smart.

1243
01:37:35,586 --> 01:37:37,281
Can you bomb Tent No. 3 with that?

1244
01:37:49,366 --> 01:37:50,458
What is this?

1245
01:37:50,568 --> 01:37:51,694
Sana.

1246
01:37:54,505 --> 01:37:55,665
Chitti.

1247
01:37:58,475 --> 01:37:59,703
Sana.

1248
01:38:00,110 --> 01:38:02,738
The beautiful girl who
compels machines to love.

1249
01:38:05,783 --> 01:38:06,875
What?

1250
01:38:06,951 --> 01:38:10,387
Her touch turns a
machine into a human.

1251
01:38:10,554 --> 01:38:12,613
And a human turns into a machine.

1252
01:38:12,756 --> 01:38:14,189
Chitti, what is this? Throw it.

1253
01:38:14,258 --> 01:38:17,056
Her tresses are like
a black waterfall.

1254
01:38:18,762 --> 01:38:21,822
Her forehead is like a piece of moon.

1255
01:38:23,267 --> 01:38:27,363
Her eyes are like a deep blue
sea which can drown the world.

1256
01:38:29,406 --> 01:38:32,807
Her lips are like soft rose petals.

1257
01:38:36,180 --> 01:38:39,581
Her waist that sways like a serpent.

1258
01:38:42,286 --> 01:38:43,878
And..
- Chitti, stop it.

1259
01:38:44,154 --> 01:38:45,678
What nonsense is this,
Dr. Vaseegaran?

1260
01:38:45,990 --> 01:38:47,821
Instead of fighting a war,
this robot is reciting poetry.

1261
01:38:47,925 --> 01:38:49,222
I'm sorry, General.

1262
01:38:49,326 --> 01:38:52,523
Friends, drop your arms
and catch stoles instead.

1263
01:38:53,230 --> 01:38:56,165
Forget the cannons and
fall in love with someone.

1264
01:38:56,233 --> 01:38:57,632
Why should we fight a war?
- Chitti?

1265
01:38:57,701 --> 01:38:59,191
What are these weapons for?

1266
01:38:59,403 --> 01:39:02,668
Love is something that
turns foes into friends.

1267
01:39:05,542 --> 01:39:07,373
Wow. Mr. Sinha, I want you all to see..
- Chitti, don't embarrass me further.

1268
01:39:07,544 --> 01:39:09,341
No war, only love.

1269
01:39:09,713 --> 01:39:11,806
Stupid scientist, stupid machine.
- Waste of time.

1270
01:39:15,953 --> 01:39:17,511
You ruined my reputation.

1271
01:39:17,588 --> 01:39:19,419
Doctor, what are you doing?

1272
01:39:19,857 --> 01:39:21,415
You destroyed my dreams.

1273
01:39:22,393 --> 01:39:24,020
Doctor, don't hit me.

1274
01:39:24,094 --> 01:39:25,891
I treated you as my son.

1275
01:39:29,500 --> 01:39:30,660
I want to live.

1276
01:39:31,101 --> 01:39:32,329
Let me live.

1277
01:39:32,569 --> 01:39:33,695
Please.

1278
01:39:33,771 --> 01:39:36,331
I won't let a useless machine
like you live in this world.

1279
01:39:36,674 --> 01:39:38,107
I will destroy it.

1280
01:39:39,476 --> 01:39:40,636
What's my mistake?

1281
01:39:40,711 --> 01:39:42,269
It's all my fault.

1282
01:39:45,449 --> 01:39:47,041
Did I tell you to make me?

1283
01:39:47,918 --> 01:39:49,613
Did I tell you to give me emotions?

1284
01:39:51,488 --> 01:39:53,217
Did I tell Sana to kiss me?

1285
01:39:54,191 --> 01:39:55,317
You..

1286
01:39:57,327 --> 01:39:58,658
You did all this.

1287
01:39:59,063 --> 01:40:00,325
Now I want to live.

1288
01:40:00,998 --> 01:40:03,489
You are killing me.
This is injustice.

1289
01:40:06,036 --> 01:40:07,333
Shut up.

1290
01:40:11,241 --> 01:40:13,266
Spare me. I want to live.

1291
01:40:14,144 --> 01:40:16,942
I want to love. I love Sana.

1292
01:40:21,752 --> 01:40:23,344
I want Sana.

1293
01:40:24,354 --> 01:40:26,185
I love Sana.

1294
01:41:29,353 --> 01:41:31,981
Forget it, Vasee. I am
also feeling sad about it.

1295
01:41:32,856 --> 01:41:34,881
For how long will you stay
like this remembering him?

1296
01:41:36,693 --> 01:41:38,820
Chitti is gone, so let him.
It is just a machine.

1297
01:41:39,296 --> 01:41:40,786
You are a great scientist.

1298
01:41:41,098 --> 01:41:42,861
You can make many
more Chittis like him.

1299
01:41:43,867 --> 01:41:45,994
I never considered
Chitti as a machine, Sana.

1300
01:41:46,603 --> 01:41:48,230
I have brought you out so
that you can forget him.

1301
01:41:48,305 --> 01:41:49,897
And all you are doing
is thinking about him.

1302
01:41:50,007 --> 01:41:51,440
You have to snap out of it.

1303
01:41:51,508 --> 01:41:53,271
Divert your mind.

1304
01:41:54,411 --> 01:41:55,969
Chitti was my life time achievement.

1305
01:41:56,079 --> 01:41:57,546
My 10 years' hard work.

1306
01:42:08,625 --> 01:42:10,252
Come, let's go for a walk.

1307
01:42:12,329 --> 01:42:14,058
Are you coming to the
beach with me or not?

1308
01:42:14,398 --> 01:42:16,263
I don't feel like it.
You go ahead, Sana.

1309
01:42:16,700 --> 01:42:19,635
If you don't come with me, I
will surely stop loving you.

1310
01:42:22,573 --> 01:42:23,733
Okay, I will go alone.

1311
01:42:23,841 --> 01:42:25,900
I will make the first
man I meet my boyfriend.

1312
01:42:33,217 --> 01:42:34,411
Hello.

1313
01:42:36,019 --> 01:42:37,247
Hi.

1314
01:42:40,057 --> 01:42:42,753
Hello. Wait. Listen.

1315
01:42:43,727 --> 01:42:44,921
What is your name?

1316
01:42:44,995 --> 01:42:46,019
Bachimohan.

1317
01:42:46,296 --> 01:42:48,662
Bachi, will you be my
boyfriend for a day?

1318
01:42:49,233 --> 01:42:51,133
Boyfriend for a day?
- Yes.

1319
01:42:51,401 --> 01:42:52,026
Like in the movie 'Nayak'
(Indian movie) the hero..

1320
01:42:52,169 --> 01:42:53,227
..was made the CM for one day.

1321
01:42:53,303 --> 01:42:54,668
Similarly, I want you to
be my boyfriend for a day.

1322
01:42:54,771 --> 01:42:57,262
Oh, God. You are fair and beautiful.
I am dark and ugly.

1323
01:42:57,341 --> 01:43:00,037
I will be your boyfriend?
- Yes.

1324
01:43:01,211 --> 01:43:03,907
How should I thank you?
I cannot believe it.

1325
01:43:03,981 --> 01:43:06,472
It's like hitting a jackpot of
1 billion sitting back home.

1326
01:43:06,750 --> 01:43:08,945
Okay, what gift are you
giving your girlfriend?

1327
01:43:09,019 --> 01:43:12,079
There is country liquor,
dry fish.. Have some. - Okay.

1328
01:43:18,629 --> 01:43:19,926
Cheers.

1329
01:43:32,643 --> 01:43:35,134
Have some and experience the high.
- No, thanks.

1330
01:43:35,746 --> 01:43:37,077
Can I have some?

1331
01:43:43,120 --> 01:43:44,587
It's useless.

1332
01:43:45,122 --> 01:43:47,056
Okay, Bachi. I'll make a move.

1333
01:43:48,492 --> 01:43:50,756
Hey, why did you catch my hand?

1334
01:43:51,828 --> 01:43:54,490
Come on. You made me
your boyfriend for a day.

1335
01:43:54,564 --> 01:43:56,031
You enkindled desires in me.

1336
01:43:56,133 --> 01:43:57,930
How can you leave now?
- Disgusting.

1337
01:43:58,001 --> 01:43:59,366
My boyfriend is over there.

1338
01:43:59,436 --> 01:44:00,801
I said all that to make him jealous.

1339
01:44:01,004 --> 01:44:02,301
Let go. Let go of my hand.

1340
01:44:02,406 --> 01:44:03,600
What do you think I am?

1341
01:44:03,907 --> 01:44:05,704
Come on, satisfy by desires quietly.

1342
01:44:05,809 --> 01:44:07,902
Let go. Vasee.

1343
01:44:08,645 --> 01:44:09,737
Vasee.

1344
01:44:09,846 --> 01:44:11,074
Why are you calling Vasee?

1345
01:44:11,148 --> 01:44:12,979
Hey, are you calling your man?

1346
01:44:13,283 --> 01:44:14,511
I won't let go of you
no matter who comes.

1347
01:44:14,584 --> 01:44:15,676
Vasee.

1348
01:44:16,920 --> 01:44:18,080
Vasee, come.

1349
01:44:18,789 --> 01:44:19,983
Now.

1350
01:44:21,191 --> 01:44:22,453
Let go of her.

1351
01:44:22,759 --> 01:44:24,989
She is my girlfriend for today.

1352
01:44:25,062 --> 01:44:26,222
You can come tomorrow.

1353
01:44:26,330 --> 01:44:27,729
Hey, I will kill you.

1354
01:44:27,798 --> 01:44:29,789
Hey, I will slice you up.

1355
01:44:29,866 --> 01:44:31,595
Police. Police.
- Police.

1356
01:44:31,668 --> 01:44:32,828
Help. Help.

1357
01:44:32,903 --> 01:44:34,427
Hey, I know the IG
(Inspector General).

1358
01:44:34,504 --> 01:44:36,631
Look, I will call him
up and get you arrested.

1359
01:44:36,707 --> 01:44:39,403
Hey, I will never get such a beau
tiful girl in my life.

1360
01:44:39,476 --> 01:44:42,411
I am ready to spend the rest
of my life in prison for her.

1361
01:44:42,479 --> 01:44:44,037
Call anyone you want.
Go ahead and call him.

1362
01:44:44,114 --> 01:44:46,082
God. It would have been so
nice if Chitti was here.

1363
01:44:46,149 --> 01:44:47,309
He would've broken all his bones.

1364
01:44:47,617 --> 01:44:49,141
Now why are you
reminding me of Chitti?

1365
01:44:50,654 --> 01:44:52,087
Vasee, do something.

1366
01:44:52,789 --> 01:44:54,051
Now there is only one option left.

1367
01:44:54,124 --> 01:44:56,524
What?
- One. Two..

1368
01:44:57,594 --> 01:44:58,822
Three.

1369
01:45:00,630 --> 01:45:01,824
Escape.

1370
01:45:03,166 --> 01:45:04,724
Not bad.
- Run. Run.

1371
01:50:52,182 --> 01:50:53,843
Chitti cannot be
connected through virtual call.

1372
01:50:53,917 --> 01:50:55,009
What happened?

1373
01:50:55,118 --> 01:50:57,109
Chitti was dismantled and thrown
in the garbage after..

1374
01:50:57,187 --> 01:50:58,381
..the army evaluation, sir.

1375
01:50:58,988 --> 01:51:00,512
We don't keep 2-days' old junk here.

1376
01:51:00,590 --> 01:51:02,751
Sir, it must have been
thrown out of the city by now.

1377
01:51:02,826 --> 01:51:03,952
Where?
- Dharamgudi.

1378
01:51:10,967 --> 01:51:13,527
Sana, what did you do to
make him change his mind?

1379
01:51:15,171 --> 01:51:16,832
When should we fix the wedding?

1380
01:51:17,374 --> 01:51:18,864
I still haven't done much, Father.

1381
01:51:18,975 --> 01:51:20,101
I'll make another robot and..

1382
01:51:20,243 --> 01:51:22,609
I'll kill you if you
mention robot again.

1383
01:51:23,146 --> 01:51:25,944
Son, isn't one
broken television enough?

1384
01:51:26,683 --> 01:51:29,015
Uncle, give me a wedding
necklace if you have one.

1385
01:51:29,119 --> 01:51:30,245
We'll get over with it right away.

1386
01:51:30,387 --> 01:51:31,945
Okay. Okay. I understand your worry.

1387
01:51:32,122 --> 01:51:33,919
Do one thing. Exchange rings for now.

1388
01:51:33,990 --> 01:51:35,252
We will get you married on
the next auspicious date.

1389
01:52:27,544 --> 01:52:28,670
Hey.

1390
01:52:33,950 --> 01:52:38,319
Help. Help.

1391
01:52:39,088 --> 01:52:42,751
Take me to Professor Bora's lab.

1392
01:52:45,995 --> 01:52:50,227
Address. A-417, Niketan Colony.

1393
01:52:50,867 --> 01:52:52,698
The world is so small, Chitti.

1394
01:52:59,108 --> 01:53:01,576
I want to live.

1395
01:53:03,146 --> 01:53:05,580
I want to love.

1396
01:53:05,982 --> 01:53:07,847
I love Sana.

1397
01:53:09,986 --> 01:53:14,389
Help me, Professor. Please.

1398
01:53:15,124 --> 01:53:18,025
Make me as I was before.

1399
01:53:18,628 --> 01:53:20,220
I want to live.

1400
01:53:20,663 --> 01:53:22,858
I want Sana.

1401
01:53:24,234 --> 01:53:26,395
And I want your neural schema.

1402
01:53:26,469 --> 01:53:28,664
You can take whatever you want.

1403
01:53:29,272 --> 01:53:31,900
Make me the Chitti I was, please.

1404
01:53:33,910 --> 01:53:35,104
I will, Chitti.

1405
01:53:36,112 --> 01:53:37,272
Don't worry.

1406
01:54:14,918 --> 01:54:17,751
What's this red chip? It
doesn't belong to Chitti.

1407
01:54:18,488 --> 01:54:19,750
This is Bora's touch.

1408
01:54:20,356 --> 01:54:22,790
Additional program for Chitti.

1409
01:54:23,259 --> 01:54:24,385
Destruction program.

1410
01:54:33,469 --> 01:54:36,267
Vaseegaran gave him the
power to protect 100 humans.

1411
01:54:37,574 --> 01:54:40,509
I am giving him the
destructive powers of 100 humans.

1412
01:54:42,345 --> 01:54:45,542
In short, he is a demon now.

1413
01:54:46,616 --> 01:54:47,947
I am feeling scared, Professor.

1414
01:54:48,051 --> 01:54:49,177
Why are you changing all this?

1415
01:54:49,385 --> 01:54:51,945
Business. This is my business trial.

1416
01:54:52,388 --> 01:54:57,018
Business?
- My money and Vasee's defamation.

1417
01:55:47,644 --> 01:55:50,909
Thank you, Bora.
- Have a good time, Chitti.

1418
01:55:50,980 --> 01:55:52,470
I am going to meet Sana.

1419
01:55:52,782 --> 01:55:54,181
Sana won't be at home.

1420
01:55:54,617 --> 01:55:56,016
She must be at Raja Muthiah Hall.

1421
01:55:56,185 --> 01:55:59,814
Why? - Vaseegaran and Sana
are getting married today.

1422
01:56:24,414 --> 01:56:26,211
Chitti, how did you come here..

1423
01:56:28,418 --> 01:56:31,410
Upgraded. Version 2.0.

1424
01:56:34,357 --> 01:56:35,722
Chitti, let go of my hand.

1425
01:56:35,825 --> 01:56:37,122
Chitti, what's this?

1426
01:56:37,460 --> 01:56:38,654
Hey, Chitti. Stop.

1427
01:56:40,363 --> 01:56:41,660
Vasee.

1428
01:56:45,468 --> 01:56:46,799
Chitti.

1429
01:56:47,336 --> 01:56:49,099
No matter how much you force me..

1430
01:56:49,172 --> 01:56:52,232
..I love Vaseegaran and will
spend my life only with him.

1431
01:56:54,110 --> 01:56:55,702
Only if he stays alive.

1432
01:57:01,384 --> 01:57:04,842
Kill me before you kill Vaseegaran.

1433
01:57:06,456 --> 01:57:07,787
Vasee.

1434
01:57:18,768 --> 01:57:20,565
I spared his life because of you.

1435
01:57:27,176 --> 01:57:29,576
Move.
- Chitti, what are you doing?

1436
01:57:30,313 --> 01:57:31,780
Stop it.

1437
01:57:44,393 --> 01:57:46,190
Car no. TN09 BB11.

1438
01:58:03,946 --> 01:58:05,743
Help me. Please.

1439
01:58:08,417 --> 01:58:10,385
Madam, come out fast.

1440
01:58:11,521 --> 01:58:13,648
Give me your hand. Come on. Move.

1441
02:01:56,078 --> 02:01:57,705
Happy 'Diwali'
(Festival of lights), folks.

1442
02:02:50,866 --> 02:02:52,458
What sort of robot have you made?

1443
02:02:52,768 --> 02:02:54,030
Do you know how many policemen died..

1444
02:02:54,103 --> 02:02:55,229
..and how much destruction he caused?

1445
02:02:55,337 --> 02:02:56,463
You are responsible for all this.

1446
02:02:56,539 --> 02:02:57,836
We will take action against you.

1447
02:02:58,240 --> 02:03:00,071
Sir, this is not the
robot that I created.

1448
02:03:00,676 --> 02:03:03,110
I destroyed it with my own
hands and threw it in the dustbin.

1449
02:03:03,846 --> 02:03:05,074
Even I'm not able to
understand anything.

1450
02:03:05,147 --> 02:03:07,047
First of all, we have to
find that robot and stop it.

1451
02:03:07,116 --> 02:03:08,913
You tell me some way.
- We have to find it.

1452
02:03:08,984 --> 02:03:10,611
That's my responsibility.
Give me a minute.

1453
02:03:12,755 --> 02:03:15,918
Why did you disturb me?
- Chitti, what happened to you?

1454
02:03:15,991 --> 02:03:17,253
Your system has completely corrupted.

1455
02:03:17,359 --> 02:03:18,553
I have to troubleshoot you.

1456
02:03:18,627 --> 02:03:20,424
Come to the lab with Sana.
- Never.

1457
02:03:20,663 --> 02:03:22,221
I won't take your orders anymore.

1458
02:03:22,565 --> 02:03:24,226
Hey, don't forget that I created you.

1459
02:03:24,366 --> 02:03:25,924
And then you
destroyed me with hatred.

1460
02:03:26,435 --> 02:03:27,834
Now I have got
nothing to do with you.

1461
02:03:28,337 --> 02:03:30,464
I am about to marry
Sana and start a new life.

1462
02:03:30,739 --> 02:03:32,138
Now you don't disturb me.

1463
02:03:32,441 --> 02:03:34,432
Hey, what makes you so arrogant?

1464
02:03:34,510 --> 02:03:35,738
After all you are a machine.

1465
02:03:36,011 --> 02:03:38,639
If I can make you, I
can also destroy you.

1466
02:03:39,248 --> 02:03:41,079
So come here with Sana
without making any fuss.

1467
02:03:53,963 --> 02:03:55,954
No one can destroy me.

1468
02:04:12,114 --> 02:04:14,514
Sir, cash, cheque or credit card?

1469
02:04:14,583 --> 02:04:15,880
Gun.

1470
02:04:17,486 --> 02:04:19,317
All the policemen doing
the rounds in South Chennai..

1471
02:04:19,388 --> 02:04:21,720
..shall block all the roads
of T Nagar and keep a check.

1472
02:04:29,598 --> 02:04:31,896
Move aside. Run.

1473
02:04:39,808 --> 02:04:41,639
Chitti is fleeing after
robbing City Center Mall.

1474
02:04:41,710 --> 02:04:43,439
Seal all the nearby
areas of Mahilapur.

1475
02:04:43,512 --> 02:04:45,104
Let's go to Dr. Radhakrishna road.
- Okay, sir.

1476
02:04:58,227 --> 02:05:01,560
Catch him. Someone
stop him. Catch him.

1477
02:05:01,630 --> 02:05:03,393
We got the message
that Chitti has entered..

1478
02:05:03,465 --> 02:05:05,023
..Ennur petrol filling station.

1479
02:05:08,003 --> 02:05:11,404
Stop. Hey, stop.

1480
02:05:27,990 --> 02:05:29,981
The robot has gone into breakwaters.
- Good.

1481
02:05:30,359 --> 02:05:32,190
You keep following him
maintaining some distance.

1482
02:05:32,428 --> 02:05:34,020
Coast guards will
take care of the rest.

1483
02:05:47,576 --> 02:05:50,670
We had to take this risk. If
we hadn't destroyed Chitti..

1484
02:05:50,746 --> 02:05:52,577
..people would've faced more damage.

1485
02:05:52,715 --> 02:05:55,240
Wasn't there any other
safer way to destroy Chitti?

1486
02:05:55,351 --> 02:05:57,012
It's so difficult
to catch one person.

1487
02:05:57,119 --> 02:05:59,212
Can you imagine how difficult
it is to catch a robot who is..

1488
02:05:59,355 --> 02:06:00,947
..equivalent to 100 men?

1489
02:06:01,023 --> 02:06:03,253
Who is the head of this operation?
- Commissioner.

1490
02:06:04,026 --> 02:06:05,459
This is not Chitti.
- What?

1491
02:06:06,262 --> 02:06:07,661
This is not the robot that I created.

1492
02:06:07,763 --> 02:06:08,923
All the parts are different.

1493
02:06:09,465 --> 02:06:10,591
Even I don't understand.

1494
02:06:10,799 --> 02:06:12,426
He stole at four
places simultaneously.

1495
02:06:12,735 --> 02:06:14,635
And they are in four
different corners of the city.

1496
02:06:14,703 --> 02:06:16,933
How is it possible for
one man to do all this?

1497
