02:39:24,358 --> 02:39:26,349
..due to its limitless
power and intelligence.

1745
02:39:26,426 --> 02:39:28,417
And we can't overlook the danger..

1746
02:39:28,495 --> 02:39:31,089
..of it being used wrongly either.

1747
02:39:31,231 --> 02:39:35,065
An advanced robot like him
may be useful in the future.

1748
02:39:35,335 --> 02:39:38,930
But we don't need it in today's life.

1749
02:39:39,039 --> 02:39:42,668
That's why the court
bans this robot forever.

1750
02:39:49,716 --> 02:39:53,584
The court orders to
dismantle every part of this robot..

1751
02:39:53,687 --> 02:39:55,917
..in the presence of
the district magistrate..

1752
02:39:55,989 --> 02:39:58,583
..and police
commissioner and inform the court.

1753
02:39:59,726 --> 02:40:01,216
Dismantle it.

1754
02:40:14,441 --> 02:40:16,170
You need any help, doctor?

1755
02:40:18,979 --> 02:40:21,846
Dismantle yourself, Chitti.
- Sure, doctor.

1756
02:40:29,356 --> 02:40:30,983
Shiva, Ravi.

1757
02:40:31,658 --> 02:40:34,388
You said that you've a
special thing that I don't.

1758
02:40:34,661 --> 02:40:36,822
See how many problems it created?

1759
02:40:40,300 --> 02:40:42,097
I mean feelings.

1760
02:40:45,205 --> 02:40:46,331
Don't cry.

1761
02:40:46,673 --> 02:40:48,641
Sister Lata. How is your son now?

1762
02:40:49,242 --> 02:40:50,869
I have named him after you, Chitti.

1763
02:40:52,546 --> 02:40:53,979
Mother gave me that name.

1764
02:40:54,081 --> 02:40:55,309
Educate him a lot.

1765
02:40:55,549 --> 02:40:57,779
Robotics. There's a
huge scope in future.

1766
02:41:01,822 --> 02:41:05,815
Professor Bora, just like you
installed a red chip in me..

1767
02:41:06,326 --> 02:41:10,763
..similarly every human carries
such red chips of lies, envy..

1768
02:41:10,831 --> 02:41:13,231
..deceit and dishonesty in his heart.

1769
02:41:13,900 --> 02:41:16,368
Thankfully I am not human.

1770
02:41:17,371 --> 02:41:20,067
Otherwise I could've never got
rid of it even if I wanted to.

1771
02:41:22,943 --> 02:41:24,706
I've tormented you a lot.

1772
02:41:25,612 --> 02:41:27,341
I am extremely sorry, Sana.

1773
02:41:28,582 --> 02:41:31,380
Hey, why are you all so upset?

1774
02:41:31,952 --> 02:41:33,544
Let me tell you a joke.

1775
02:41:34,187 --> 02:41:36,781
It's said that love
makes a person lose his head.

1776
02:41:37,958 --> 02:41:38,947
Look.

1777
02:41:39,025 --> 02:41:40,492
It's the same with me.

1778
02:41:43,230 --> 02:41:44,925
I am going to miss you, Sana.

1779
02:41:46,032 --> 02:41:47,294
Not a boyfriend.

1780
02:41:48,301 --> 02:41:49,859
As a toy-friend.

1781
02:41:52,839 --> 02:41:55,865
Doctor, you're my God.

1782
02:41:56,376 --> 02:41:58,071
I betrayed you.

1783
02:41:58,311 --> 02:41:59,869
It was my mistake to break the rules.

1784
02:41:59,946 --> 02:42:02,210
Forgive me.
- No, Chitti.

1785
02:42:03,016 --> 02:42:05,507
You learnt to break
rules from humans.

1786
02:42:06,286 --> 02:42:08,220
It's not just your mistake.

1787
02:42:09,589 --> 02:42:11,216
Thank you, doctor.

1788
02:42:16,096 --> 02:42:17,961
I am feeling good, doctor.

1789
02:42:37,717 --> 02:42:39,776
Be sure you're not touching anything.

1790
02:42:41,788 --> 02:42:45,519
Children, you're looking at Chitti.

1791
02:42:45,792 --> 02:42:48,352
The most advanced
andro-humanized robot.

1792
02:42:49,129 --> 02:42:52,496
20 years ago, Dr.
Vaseegaran had built him.

1793
02:42:52,766 --> 02:42:56,099
And then it was
dismantled after a while.

1794
02:42:56,703 --> 02:42:57,897
Why?

1795
02:42:58,338 --> 02:42:59,930
I started thinking.

1796
02:43:02,075 --> 02:43:04,543
Okay, children. Come

